OL,3,CSaints lose 2-1 to Manchester City in
OL,4,CFA Cup semi-final at Wembley
OL,6,FSouthampton fans are heading home
OL,7,Fafter suffering a 2-1 defeat to
OL,8,FManchester City in the FA Cup semi-
OL,9,Ffinal at Wembley.
OL,11,FMore than 37,000 Saints supporters
OL,12,Ftravelled to the capital, hoping the
OL,13,Fyellow army would replicate their
OL,14,Ffamous FA Cup win of 1976.
OL,16,FSouthampton took the lead early on in
OL,17,Fthe second half leading 1-0.
OL,19,FBut it wasn't to be.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/2
