OL,6,FManchester City quickly equalised with
OL,7,Fa goal minutes later and then a second
OL,8,Fgoal.
OL,10,FMore follows.....
OL,12,FThe last time Southampton made an FA
OL,13,FCup final was 2003, but the team lost
OL,14,F1-0 to Arsenal.
